    SetStencilReferenceValue
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>SetStencilReferenceValue</TypeRef> method sets the reference value which will be used when performing stencil testing.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void SetStencilReferenceValue(uint32_t referenceValue);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="uint32_t" Name="referenceValue">
          The reference value used by the active stencil comparison function.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
